$MUDNAME$ player help
pub

.SH Name
.SI 5
pub - a place where you can buy food and drink
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
buy <drink|food>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
A nice place that gives a choice of alcoholic or other sorts of beverages
to buy.  A pub can sell both food and drink.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> buy beer
> buy stew
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
pub shop
.EP
